	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Curavi describi, quae dilectus frater <persName ref="p8033">Beza</persName> ad me scripsit, eaque tibi communicari vouit; idem te salutat amicissime.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Cardinalis Lotharingius</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Galliae</placeName> rex, totus in hoc est, ut celebretur concilium, sed subdolis rationibus, de quo nunc non est ocium scribendi.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mittitur modo ad imperatorem tanquam a <persName type="auto_name" ref="p8347">rege Galliae</persName> legatus d. <persName type="auto_name">Sancti Laurentii</persName>, qui scriptis ad me literis a <persName type="auto_name">Schaffhusio</persName> ex itinere non dissimulat causam legationis etc.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus dissipet impiorum concilia atque [consi]lia!</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mittuntur et ad principes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822">Germaniae</placeName> nuncii etc.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego vero, qui mature admonitus ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834">Italia</placeName> consilii Achitophelici, illustrissimo principi <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3590">Hessorum</persName> rem detexi; nam miserat is ad me nuncium his diebus, per quem significavit, quid moliantur theologi Ienenses persuadere <placeName ref="l572">Wirtenbergensi</placeName> et aliis principibus, ut synodum conscribant, in quo adiaphor[istae] et sacramentarii <persName type="auto_name">Zvingliani</persName> damnentur etc.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero dominum impia istorum consilia dispersurum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi [ex] <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglia</placeName> literas datas sub finem maii et medi[um iunii] testantes pulchre per dei gratiam procedere re[ligionem], <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglos</placeName> sociale bellum gerere in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524">Scotia</placeName> [contra] <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Gallos</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Aliquamdiu actum de pace; nil [tamen] ea de re addiderunt, sed libellos potius eo tempore <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l296">Londini</placeName> excusos, alterum regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Galliae</placeName> protestationem, alterum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18554">reginae Angliae</persName> resposionem, in quibus agitur, quo iure quave iniuria bellum utrinque geratur etc.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus concedat pacem!</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnia ubique turbulenta sunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Papistici episcopi in <placeName ref="l830" type="citizen_name">Anglia</placeName> superioribus diebus in carcerem plures coniecti sunt etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Libellum, cuius meminit <persName ref="p8033">Beza</persName> de tumultu <persName type="auto_name">Ambosiano</persName> tabelliones mihi non dederunt.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta d. <persName ref="p7175">Matthiam</persName>, cui haec communicabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tiguri</placeName> 12. iulii 1560. festinantissime.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Bullingerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8055">Ambrosio Blaurero</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l555">Vituduri</placeName> agenti, domino suo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Gen <placeName ref="l555">Wintherdur</placeName> an m. <persName ref="p8055">Ambrosien Blaureren</persName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
